Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}在暗黑中寻找我的路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.11,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Feeling my way through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}让跃动的心领导
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Guided by a beating heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}我说不出哪里是这趟旅行的终点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.15,0:00:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}I can’t tell where the journey will end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}但我知道这是在哪里开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}But I know where it starts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}他们告诉我，我不懂，因为太年轻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}They tell me I’m too young to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}他们告诉我，我已迷失在梦中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}They say I’m caught up in a dream
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}若我不苏醒，时间便会擦身而过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Well life will pass me by if I don’t open up my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}好吧，我已经找到它了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}Well that’s fine by me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}所以当这一切结束时，请叫醒我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}So wake me up when it’s all over
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}当我长大，更有智慧了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1}When I’m wiser and I’m older
